The Brotherhood of Railway andAirline Clerks said more than 5,500 former Republic Airlinesworkers will receive an average of 10,000 dlrs each as part ofa stock payout.    It said some members will receive almost 19,000 dlrs inpayments.    The total 56 mln dlr payment comes from an employee stockownership plan negotiated by several unions representingRepublic employees before the carrier's takeover by &lt;NorthwestAirlines> in 1986, it said. Reuter&#3;